    "multicolumn_VTPptV": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_QY3yzd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_90.png",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<strong>These Saved My Life!</strong>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>★★★★★</p><p>These flip flops saved my summer! My plantar fasciitis was really bad and when I put these on I felt relief almost immediately. The discomfort continues to subside more and more each day, and is still improving, which I largely attribute to wearing these all day, every day. Plus, they felt very secure even when wet. Very thankful for these!</p><p><em>- Lisa R.</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_R8g7jX": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_91.png",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<strong>My Absolute Favorite!</strong>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>★★★★★</p><p>These were the first shoe I ordered from Aetrex. I loved them immediately. I am now on my 3rd pair, including one for my daughter since she kept stealing mine! They are cushiony & supportive enough for a day at an amusement park plus the strap keeps them secure. Casual enough for everyday, but dressy enough for a night out means only packing one pair for trips.</p><p><em>- Holly J.</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_kMKiDg": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_92.png",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<strong>Better Than My Bare Feet!</strong>",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>★★★★★</p><p>These sandals are perfect. They are very cushioned and supportive in all the right places. I can already feel the difference with my pronation issues when I wear these slides. I also love that they are cute and so easy to wear. I wear them out or just around the house. I couldn't recommend more!!!</p><p><em>- Kimberly S.</em></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
